('Basic Geometry', 'Area/Perimeter', 'Perimeter', 'Choose the correct answer.', 'Find the perimeter of a square with side 6 cm.', '24 cm', '36 cm', '18 cm', '12 cm', 'Perimeter of square = 4 × side = 4 × 6 = 24 cm'),
