('Basic Geometry', 'Area/Perimeter', 'Area', 'Choose the correct answer.', 'Find the area of a circle with radius 7 cm. (Use π ≈ 3.14)', '153.86 cm²', '140 cm²', '150 cm²', '160 cm²', 'Area = πr² = 3.14 × 7² = 3.14 × 49 = 153.86 cm²'),
('Basic Geometry', 'Area/Perimeter', 'Perimeter', 'Choose the correct answer.', 'Find the perimeter of a rectangle with length 10 m and width 6 m.', '32 m', '28 m', '30 m', '36 m', 'Perimeter = 2(length + width) = 2(10+6)=32 m'),
